nA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-24/poem-rrYJZBWukSn78Tnyz4BNFw">Thủ 24 - 首２４</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/Th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-C%C3%BAc-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Qx0tgzKdHgbmPhUBW2JlQg">Thư hoài phụng trình Cúc Đường chủ nhân - 書懷奉呈菊堂主人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nguy%C3%AAn-%E1%BB%A9ng-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-IuY5ty-lKqSV9eUw78nM9Q">Thượng nguyên ứng chế - 上元應制</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/author-IRXLchCCp9FCax7d5XFTCQ">Vương Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4ng-ph%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-AVg8Skt8920Y3Be0N6PH8Q">Tông phất tử - 棕拂子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
